.TH HEX2BIN 1 "2026-05-18" "f9dasm 1.83" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hex2bin \- convert Intel Hex records to a raw binary file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hex2bin
.RI [ \-out
.IR file ]
.I file.hex
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hex2bin
reads an Intel Hex\-formatted file and writes the decoded data as a raw
binary stream.
.PP
It is shipped as a companion utility to
.BR f9dasm (1)
for preparing raw binary input from common ROM dump formats.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-out " file"
Write the binary output to
.IR file
instead of standard output.
.SH EXAMPLES
Convert
.I rom.hex
to
.IR rom.bin :
.IP
.B hex2bin \-out rom.bin rom.hex
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR f9dasm (1),
.BR mot2bin (1),
.BR cmd2mot (1)
.SH AUTHORS
Part of the
.B f9dasm
suite by Arto Salmi, Hermann Seib, Colin Bourassa, and Rainer Buchty.
